{"tid":1069400,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"手剁蓮藕餅 【老娘的草根飯堂】","createTime":"2019-03-20T03:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T08:19:35.000Z","uid":30742,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8ddb72bfa5a0dee53dbc0d6d67d63dee6de1ac2e","tid":1069400,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AeSB44C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAeSB44C.jpg&h=eac29552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vJMy3_GaXkI  \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvJMy3_GaXkI%20%20&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9IICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=ecfc4b3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vJMy3_GaXkI  </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係之前某巴打點菜既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！(我本身好少做餅，多數做蓮藕夾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n我做左幾次，呢次我覺得做得最好！最簡單，最好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個人鍾意蓮藕同肉大概六四比，肉剛剛夠黏蓮藕就好！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落去爽爽脆脆的！ <br />\n而且一次可以做多點放冰格，朝早返工放下格 放工返去就煎得喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n圖文食譜  手剁蓮藕餅: <br />\n<a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2019/03/lotus-root-mini-cakes.html \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F03%2Flotus-root-mini-cakes.html%20&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9IICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=d11ac349\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol